  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/e53500d64a50dbbe4c13b5be467151f8.poster.avif?t=1744515472\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/e53500d64a50dbbe4c13b5be467151f8.webm?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/e53500d64a50dbbe4c13b5be467151f8.mp4?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"FUBUKI ~zero in on Holoearth~\" is a high-speed pixel action game where you control the protagonist, \"Shirakami Fubuki,\" and battle using swords and skills.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An exhilarating 2D pixel action adventure with Fubuki across \"Holoearth\"!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/ec016591933977c05b54146373b8b3f0.poster.avif?t=1744515472\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/ec016591933977c05b54146373b8b3f0.webm?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/ec016591933977c05b54146373b8b3f0.mp4?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You take control of \"Shirakami Fubuki,\" one of the \"Kami\" residing in \"Yamato.\"  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With her beloved sword \"Murasamemaru,\" she skillfully performs sword fights, high-speed movement, and even wall jumps with ease.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight alongside Fubuki, defeat the \"Ayakashi\" blocking your path, and resolve the anomalies occurring in \"Holoearth.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(This game is developed with reference to the world settings of the teaser PV and manga of Hololive Alternative. Please note that some content and expressions may differ from the official settings.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/4e370e76203048c63efc734f47e1cf9e.poster.avif?t=1744515472\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/4e370e76203048c63efc734f47e1cf9e.webm?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/4e370e76203048c63efc734f47e1cf9e.mp4?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of \"Holoearth\" is diverse and ever-changing.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage features a completely different appearance, enemies, and mechanics.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize your player skills and the allies you meet along the way to overcome challenging obstacles.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/5b0969c5784ab998dac4b008a617fbfb.poster.avif?t=1744515472\" width=620 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/5b0969c5784ab998dac4b008a617fbfb.webm?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/5b0969c5784ab998dac4b008a617fbfb.mp4?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your adventure, you may encounter Hololive menbers who have been corrupted by \"Kegare\" and turned hostile.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat them to restore their sanity—they will surely lend you their strength once they are back to normal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/afb396c7245e6fda19c7af1e1e645a36.poster.avif?t=1744515472\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/afb396c7245e6fda19c7af1e1e645a36.webm?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/afb396c7245e6fda19c7af1e1e645a36.mp4?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
