e been corrupted by \"Kegare\" and turned hostile.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat them to restore their sanity—they will surely lend you their strength once they are back to normal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/afb396c7245e6fda19c7af1e1e645a36.poster.avif?t=1744515472\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/afb396c7245e6fda19c7af1e1e645a36.webm?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446990/extras/afb396c7245e6fda19c7af1e1e645a36.mp4?t=1744515472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
